---
title: Cheesy Chicken Enchiladas with Sour Cream
description: Enchiladas – what could be more fun? Take one part smoky, tender chicken and one part melted cheesy goodness and top with a generous dollop of sour cream. Let the whole family chip in with this easy-to-make Mexican-inspired feast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/enchiladas-gratinees-au-poulet-5ac3526f.jpg
